{"1649950":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"News Tower","steam_appid":1649950,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"dlc":[2732720],"detailed_description":"<h1>Post-Launch Roadmap<\/h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/995e2ca0bb235a78c25ee8a1ed4d68f1.avif?t=1776945916\" data-big-src=https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras_big\/995e2ca0bb235a78c25ee8a1ed4d68f1.avif?t=1776945916 width=1560 height=3728 \/><\/span><\/p><\/p><br><h1>About the Game<\/h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/2679c1705029f21f1b84d68c2edd9ccc.webp?t=1776945916\" width=616 height=59 \/><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/c094390b6f58f809f0e6702d33c0f3ec.poster.avif?t=1776945916\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/c094390b6f58f809f0e6702d33c0f3ec.webm?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/c094390b6f58f809f0e6702d33c0f3ec.mp4?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In News Tower, dive into the chaos of <strong>1930s New York in a management tycoon game<\/strong> where you build and manage your own newspaper.   <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the Great Depression to the brink of World War II every Sunday brings a new deadline, and every article is a strategic decision. Between <strong>editorial dilemmas, newsroom breakdowns, and political pressure,<\/strong> <i>you’ll shape the future of your newspaper to start your media empire!<\/i>  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/d842518e2d7d7b06a5400257d64141a0.webp?t=1776945916\" width=616 height=59 \/><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/4d55c0a1c4f698e415df3cbe8b8de706.poster.avif?t=1776945916\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/4d55c0a1c4f698e415df3cbe8b8de706.webm?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/4d55c0a1c4f698e415df3cbe8b8de706.mp4?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Start with a blank floor and shape your newsroom from the ground up.<\/strong> As your newspaper grows, <strong>unlock new levels and transform each one into a fully functional hub of journalism.<\/strong> From printing stations and compositing desks to the legal corner for damage control, every workstation is key to keep the presses running.   <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Smart layout choices:<\/strong> walls, elevators, pneumatic tubes directly impact how efficiently your team works under pressure. And because morale matters too, add coffee machines, posters, and the essential indoor green plant to ensure your employees’ well-being!  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/71bf475cf07004c90aa26bf3f8c531e3.webp?t=1776945916\" width=616 height=59 \/><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/6c4b55e4d918108853d2e2665076fcd5.poster.avif?t=1776945916\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/6c4b55e4d918108853d2e2665076fcd5.webm?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/6c4b55e4d918108853d2e2665076fcd5.mp4?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reporters, photographers and janitors without forgetting the unexpendable ads salesperson… <strong>Lead a diverse team across 30+ unique job<\/strong> <strong>roles<\/strong> each with their own traits, needs, and expertise. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Juggle hunger, focus and logistics to maximize productivity. <strong>Unlock dozens of upgrades<\/strong> from gramophone to slot machines, to <strong>turn your dingy tower into a prestigious workspace.<\/strong> <i>A happy newsroom is a productive newsroom, especially when Sunday is always just around the corner.<\/i><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/b815b71f447fef2cf0ca10d75d2962c4.webp?t=1776945916\" width=616 height=59 \/><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/3cbbb106652b25513b51ea835d5c6fe5.poster.avif?t=1776945916\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/3cbbb106652b25513b51ea835d5c6fe5.webm?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/3cbbb106652b25513b51ea835d5c6fe5.mp4?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each week begins with one goal: getting your edition ready for Sunday’s deadline.<\/strong> Assign leads to your reporters, choose your editorial approach, influence public perception through your chosen tone and tags, and compose your newspaper.  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cover key topics like Crime, Politics, or Sports,<\/strong> and refine your story’s angle to match your editorial line. <strong>Well-researched articles or eye-grabbing headlines,<\/strong> will you aim for respect or reach?  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every choice impacts your readers’ perception, reactions, and sales. <strong>Nail the mix<\/strong> and profits soar or miss the mark and you risk backlash, lawsuits, or <i>courtesy visits<\/i> from the mob...<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/505003d227eb189f3482102175e50b59.webp?t=1776945916\" width=616 height=59 \/><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/6c17357ec0e307cc53cae931d220f2d5.poster.avif?t=1776945916\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/6c17357ec0e307cc53cae931d220f2d5.webm?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/6c17357ec0e307cc53cae931d220f2d5.mp4?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four major factions partake in the city’s power struggle: <strong>the Mayor, the Mafia, the Military (in 1.0), and High Society.<\/strong> They’ll push their own agendas and offer shady deals in exchange for cash, influence, exclusive rewards, and vital new connections across the Big Apple. Whose truth will you print, and whose secrets will you bury?  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Not everyone is in favor of freedom of the press…<\/i>  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/cf64688415274ff813c35cca5e830cf0.webp?t=1776945916\" width=616 height=59 \/><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/8be4861094a72bd929295635023efec6.poster.avif?t=1776945916\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/8be4861094a72bd929295635023efec6.webm?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/8be4861094a72bd929295635023efec6.mp4?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span> <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Publish your newspaper across NYC districts, from Harlem to Wall Street. <strong>Each borough has its own reader profiles, preferences, and rewards.<\/strong> To grow your subscriber base, tailor stories to local tastes while staying ahead of <strong>two aggressive rivals: the Empire Observer and Jersey Beacon.<\/strong> They’ll steal your precious scoops but by targeting the right interests, you can win their audiences and become New York’s most influential publisher.<\/p>","about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/2679c1705029f21f1b84d68c2edd9ccc.webp?t=1776945916\" width=616 height=59 \/><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/c094390b6f58f809f0e6702d33c0f3ec.poster.avif?t=1776945916\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/c094390b6f58f809f0e6702d33c0f3ec.webm?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/c094390b6f58f809f0e6702d33c0f3ec.mp4?t=1776945916\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In News Tower, dive into the chaos of <strong>1930s New York in a management tycoon game<\/strong> where you build and manage your own newspaper.   <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the Great Depression to the brink of World War II every Sunday brings a new deadline, and every article is a strategic decision. Between <strong>editorial dilemmas, newsroom breakdowns, and political pressure,<\/strong> <i>you’ll shape the future of your newspaper to start your media empire!<\/i>  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/d842518e2d7d7b06a5400257d64141a0.webp?t=1776945916\" width=616 height=59 \/><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1649950\/extras\/4d55c0a1c4f698e415df3cbe8b8de706.p